00:25:36.000 --> 00:25:38.279
I have no idea
what you're talking about.

269
00:25:38.280 --> 00:25:40.319
Naomi Keegan.

270
00:25:40.320 --> 00:25:42.839
And Samuel Carter.

271
00:25:42.840 --> 00:25:44.839
So. you do know them?

272
00:25:44.840 --> 00:25:46.439
Of course.

273
00:25:46.440 --> 00:25:48.520
Your wife worked for me.

274
00:25:49.920 --> 00:25:54.239
Naomi drew up the framework
for the legalisation of drugs.

275
00:25:54.240 --> 00:25:55.879
She...

276
00:25:55.880 --> 00:25:59.959
believed passionately
in everything that we are doing.

277
00:25:59.960 --> 00:26:03.799
What happened to Naomi
and your son...

278
00:26:03.800 --> 00:26:07.279
was a terrible. terrible tragedy.
No.

279
00:26:07.280 --> 00:26:09.479
You. you fucking killed them.

280
00:26:09.480 --> 00:26:13.039
Cos I know that the crash
with the truck was staged

281
00:26:13.040 --> 00:26:14.839
to look like a hit and run.
You paid them.

282
00:26:14.840 --> 00:26:16.920
You paid them to kill them.

283
00:26:18.920 --> 00:26:20.999
That was his father.

284
00:26:21.000 --> 00:26:22.879
He found out what we were doing.

285
00:26:22.880 --> 00:26:26.839
and he had Naomi killed
as a warning.

286
00:26:26.840 --> 00:26:28.479
She's fucking lying.

287
00:26:28.480 --> 00:26:30.360
Lying to save her arse.

288
00:26:32.120 --> 00:26:33.839
What the fuck!

289
00:26:33.840 --> 00:26:36.959
Don't fall
for her fucking bullshit. man.

290
00:26:36.960 --> 00:26:39.279
I admired your wife.

291
00:26:39.280 --> 00:26:41.279
I would never have hurt her.

292
00:26:41.280 --> 00:26:43.479
I'm gonna go
and find out the truth.

293
00:26:43.480 --> 00:26:46.640
Whichever one of you is lying to me.
I swear to God...

294
00:26:48.840 --> 00:26:50.679
I'll fucking kill you.

295
00:26:50.680 --> 00:26:52.440
Ugh!

296
00:27:02.120 --> 00:27:04.799
Ugh! Ugh!

297
00:27:04.800 --> 00:27:06.719
Why would you
work for the investors again.

298
00:27:06.720 --> 00:27:09.759
after what they did to Finn
and Alex?

299
00:27:09.760 --> 00:27:11.800
They left me no choice.

300
00:27:12.800 --> 00:27:15.079
They are about to legalise drugs.

301
00:27:15.080 --> 00:27:18.400
and that will mean
the end for the rest of us.

302
00:27:19.440 --> 00:27:21.639
But if you let me go.

303
00:27:21.640 --> 00:27:24.439
I promise you.
I will make sure that we...

304
00:27:24.440 --> 00:27:26.359
Wallace and Dumani...

305
00:27:26.360 --> 00:27:28.560
are part of the new order.

306
00:27:42.360 --> 00:27:44.119
Billy?

307
00:27:44.120 --> 00:27:47.600
"It was Ed's
decision to kill Sean."

308
00:27:52.400 --> 00:27:54.320
OK.

309
00:28:06.840 --> 00:28:09.280
This is for Sean.

310
00:28:10.480 --> 00:28:13.079
You...
You hadn't seen him for over a year.

311
00:28:13.080 --> 00:28:15.239
Th-The last time you saw him.

312
00:28:15.240 --> 00:28:17.279
he tried to kill you.
He was still my son.

313
00:28:17.280 --> 00:28:19.959
Don't play the grieving mother
with me. Marian.

314
00:28:19.960 --> 00:28:22.440
You never cared for your children.

315
00:28:23.920 --> 00:28:26.559
Living there.
in that cold fucking mausoleum.

316
00:28:26.560 --> 00:28:29.879
You have betrayed me
and my family for the last time.

317
00:28:34.400 --> 00:28:36.200
"Family."

318
00:28:37.440 --> 00:28:39.560
What family. Marian?

319
00:28:42.080 --> 00:28:46.240
Did you never wonder
why Finn had so many mistresses?

320
00:28:50.240 --> 00:28:52.280
You're cold. Marian.

321
00:28:56.840 --> 00:28:58.720
At least I'm dying...

322
00:28:59.960 --> 00:29:02.600
knowing that I loved...

323
00:29:04.680 --> 00:29:06.920
and I was loved.

324
00:29:09.840 --> 00:29:13.159
And that is more
than you will ever have. or-

325
00:29:52.840 --> 00:29:54.520
Please.

326
00:29:57.120 --> 00:29:59.159
Mbrapa.

327
00:29:59.160 --> 00:30:00.800
Please. Luan.

328
00:31:10.360 --> 00:31:11.480
Mum?

329
00:31:15.880 --> 00:31:18.680
Please. No. please.
He's only a child. please.

330
00:31:21.440 --> 00:31:23.959
Now you're gonna
know how you feel...

331
00:31:23.960 --> 00:31:26.640
to watch your child die
before your eyes.

332
00:31:27.800 --> 00:31:30.359
Elira's death
was a terrible mistake.

333
00:31:30.360 --> 00:31:33.159
You can kill me.
but please don't kill Danny.

334
00:31:33.160 --> 00:31:34.999
I am begging you.

335
00:31:35.000 --> 00:31:37.319
From one parent to another.

336
00:31:37.320 --> 00:31:39.600
please don't kill my baby.

337
00:31:40.880 --> 00:31:42.239
I have to.

338
00:31:42.240 --> 00:31:44.440
Luan. you don't have to. Please.

339
00:31:45.520 --> 00:31:46.919
Please.

340
00:31:53.560 --> 00:31:56.680
Ahhh!

341
00:33:44.000 --> 00:33:45.439
I'm sorry.

342
00:33:45.440 --> 00:33:47.720
It must have been difficult for you.

343
00:33:50.280 --> 00:33:52.760
What are we going to do
about Shannon and Danny?

344
00:33:54.160 --> 00:33:56.360
They're being taken care of.

345
00:33:58.560 --> 00:34:00.800
We gave our word they'd be safe.

346
00:34:01.880 --> 00:34:03.760
Danny is a kid.

347
00:34:04.840 --> 00:34:07.360
I practically grew up with Shannon.

348
00:34:08.840 --> 00:34:11.119
We gave them our word.

349
00:34:11.120 --> 00:34:12.480
Well...

350
00:34:14.640 --> 00:34:16.560
it's done.

351
00:34:28.840 --> 00:34:31.439
Do you remember years ago...

352
00:34:31.440 --> 00:34:33.840
when Dad had that lawyer killed?

353
00:34:35.400 --> 00:34:37.839
But she had her kid
in the car with her.

354
00:34:37.840 --> 00:34:40.119
And he died too.

355
00:34:40.120 --> 00:34:41.999
What of it?

356
00:34:42.000 --> 00:34:44.240
That was Elliot's wife and son.

357
00:34:48.680 --> 00:34:52.359
All this time.
I've blamed him for taking my arm.

358
00:34:52.360 --> 00:34:56.280
for putting Sean behind bars.
but what we did to him...

359
00:34:57.360 --> 00:34:59.600
it was much worse.

360
00:35:01.240 --> 00:35:03.160
Does Elliot know it was us?

361
00:35:04.280 --> 00:35:06.279
Vaughn told him it was Dad.

362
00:35:06.280 --> 00:35:08.200
But I denied it.

363
00:35:09.360 --> 00:35:10.960
So. he's not certain.

364
00:35:12.160 --> 00:35:13.880
Not yet. anyway.

365
00:35:14.840 --> 00:35:17.000
Kill him before he is certain.

366
00:35:18.520 --> 00:35:21.280
Is that the answer to everything?

367
00:35:23.080 --> 00:35:24.759
Kill Ed. Kill Shannon.

368
00:35:24.760 --> 00:35:26.239
Kill Danny.

369
00:35:26.240 --> 00:35:29.159
Kill Elliot's wife. kill his son...

370
00:35:29.160 --> 00:35:30.599
and then him?

371
00:35:30.600 --> 00:35:34.200
Would you prefer we wait
until he comes after us instead?

372
00:35:37.640 --> 00:35:41.040
If you want this life. Billy...

373
00:35:42.400 --> 00:35:46.280
you have to be capable
of making difficult decisions.

374
00:36:10.800 --> 00:36:14.759
Ed Dumani and Asif Afridi
orchestrated the spiking.

375
00:36:14.760 --> 00:36:18.079
to soften public perception.
towards the legalisation of drugs.

376
00:36:18.080 --> 00:36:19.920
Yeah. I know.

377
00:36:23.360 --> 00:36:26.400
It seems my whole career
has been about them...

378
00:36:27.480 --> 00:36:30.159
grooming me
to introduce legalisation.

379
00:36:30.160 --> 00:36:31.960
Here.

380
00:36:39.400 --> 00:36:41.679
The author of that report
is my wife.

381
00:36:41.680 --> 00:36:43.519
She knew legalisation

382
00:36:43.520 --> 00:36:45.880
was the only way to get rid
of drug-related crime.

383
00:36:46.960 --> 00:36:48.919
When they found out
what she was doing...

384
00:36:48.920 --> 00:36:52.080
they killed her and my son.

385
00:36:53.240 --> 00:36:55.360
Oh. Elliot. I'm so sorry.

386
00:36:57.760 --> 00:37:00.760
The worst part. actually...

387
00:37:02.440 --> 00:37:04.520
is that in all of this...

388
00:37:06.120 --> 00:37:08.560
I've become
what she was trying to destroy.

389
00:37:11.400 --> 00:37:13.560
I'm one of the people
that killed her.

390
00:37:17.160 --> 00:37:19.800
Use that to take down the gangs.

391
00:37:21.080 --> 00:37:22.839
No. I...

392
00:37:22.840 --> 00:37:25.039
I don't know that I can.

393
00:37:25.040 --> 00:37:27.159
Of course you can.

394
00:37:27.160 --> 00:37:29.039
Don't be like me.

395
00:37:29.040 --> 00:37:32.520
Don't lose your bearings.
Remember why you started this.

396
00:37:38.400 --> 00:37:40.240
Good luck.

397
00:37:41.360 --> 00:37:43.640
Ugh! Elliot. wait.

398
00:37:44.840 --> 00:37:46.560
Erm...

399
00:37:47.600 --> 00:37:49.280
your confession.

400
00:39:13.600 --> 00:39:15.399
Elliot. "Yeah."

401
00:39:15.400 --> 00:39:17.320
It's me.

402
00:39:18.280 --> 00:39:19.959
I need to see you.

403
00:39:19.960 --> 00:39:22.360
I think I know who killed your wife
and son.

404
00:39:24.640 --> 00:39:26.679
"Erm before
I take any questions.

405
00:39:26.680 --> 00:39:28.560
"I would like to make a statement."

406
00:39:29.640 --> 00:39:33.839
In the last few moments
I have just learned

407
00:39:33.840 --> 00:39:35.920
that my colleague. Henry Amiel...

408
00:39:36.920 --> 00:39:40.640
has been murdered...
in a gangland assassination.

409
00:39:43.680 --> 00:39:48.080
Henry was a man of integrity
and great vision.

410
00:39:53.280 --> 00:39:55.360
And someone I could always trust.

411
00:39:57.040 --> 00:40:01.119
"I'd like to offer my deepest
condolences to Henry's family

412
00:40:01.120 --> 00:40:03.960
"in their moment of profound grief."

413
00:40:05.360 --> 00:40:07.479
I believe that Henry was targeted.

414
00:40:07.480 --> 00:40:10.759
'Because he had been developing
a strategy

415
00:40:10.760 --> 00:40:16.399
'to legalise. regulate and tax
the production of illicit drugs.'

416
00:40:16.400 --> 00:40:20.239
"So. this strategy would
take the illegal drugs trade..."

417
00:40:20.240 --> 00:40:23.319
out of the hands of gangsters.

418
00:40:23.320 --> 00:40:26.599
With the Prime Minister's support...

419
00:40:26.600 --> 00:40:30.399
"I will ensure that Henry's
vision becomes a reality.

420
00:40:30.400 --> 00:40:35.359
"London will become a test case
for this initiative.

421
00:40:35.360 --> 00:40:38.480
"and if successful will be rolled
out across the country."

422
00:40:39.560 --> 00:40:41.799
"I have no doubt.
that legalisation

423
00:40:41.800 --> 00:40:44.919
"is the single
most effective weapon...

424
00:40:44.920 --> 00:40:48.519
"that we have
against organised crime gangs."

425
00:40:48.520 --> 00:40:54.119
'This initiative will significantly
weaken their power to operate.'

426
00:40:54.120 --> 00:40:57.639
And so. it is
with absolute confidence...

427
00:40:57.640 --> 00:41:01.759
"that I am putting
the gangs on notice. Your days

428
00:41:01.760 --> 00:41:04.160
"of terrorising this city...

429
00:41:05.200 --> 00:41:06.839
"are numbered."

430
00:41:34.560 --> 00:41:36.400
What did you find out?

431
00:41:41.360 --> 00:41:43.160
Sit down.

432
00:41:54.640 --> 00:41:56.880
Did I ever tell you
that when I was a kid...

433
00:41:58.280 --> 00:42:02.360
my father buried
a man up to his neck in the ground?

434
00:42:04.680 --> 00:42:06.879
He gave a gun to Sean...

435
00:42:06.880 --> 00:42:09.719
and told him to shoot him.

436
00:42:09.720 --> 00:42:12.919
Just tell me what you found.
But he couldn't.

437
00:42:12.920 --> 00:42:14.599
You don't have to do it.

438
00:42:14.600 --> 00:42:16.199
No.

439
00:42:16.200 --> 00:42:18.239
Please. No. don't please.

440
00:42:18.240 --> 00:42:20.480
He couldn't do it.

441
00:42:31.640 --> 00:42:34.120
So. I shot him instead.

442
00:42:48.480 --> 00:42:51.000
How many people have you killed.
Elliot?

443
00:42:52.640 --> 00:42:54.479
I don't know.

444
00:42:54.480 --> 00:42:56.559
Me neither.

445
00:42:56.560 --> 00:42:58.480
I've lost count.

446
00:43:01.480 --> 00:43:03.800
I've forgotten most of them.

447
00:43:05.240 --> 00:43:07.680
But there's a few I haven't.

448
00:43:08.680 --> 00:43:10.320
I can't.

449
00:43:15.800 --> 00:43:17.520
Do you want some advice?

450
00:43:19.280 --> 00:43:21.639
Get as far away from here
as you can.

451
00:43:21.640 --> 00:43:23.439
And never come back.

452
00:43:23.440 --> 00:43:25.959
Because this fucking life of ours

453
00:43:25.960 --> 00:43:28.920
takes everything you have
and it destroys it.

454
00:43:31.480 --> 00:43:35.200
Bill... I don't know what's happened
here-And you think you're winning.

455
00:43:36.240 --> 00:43:39.200
I know you do. But you can't.

456
00:43:41.160 --> 00:43:44.360
You can't win... at this game.

457
00:43:47.440 --> 00:43:49.120
Look at my dad.

458
00:43:53.320 --> 00:43:55.159
Look at Sean.

459
00:43:55.160 --> 00:43:56.879
The Dumanis.

460
00:43:56.880 --> 00:44:00.080
Even Luan's family.
all of them. fucked.

461
00:44:01.280 --> 00:44:03.120
Nobody wins.

462
00:44:04.080 --> 00:44:05.960
Nobody ever fucking wins.

463
00:44:14.960 --> 00:44:18.360
I mean. look at what
happened to your wife and son.

464
00:44:20.680 --> 00:44:23.080
Just fucking tell me.

465
00:44:33.360 --> 00:44:34.839
Kill me.

466
00:44:34.840 --> 00:44:38.319
- I'm not killing you. Bill.
- I deserve it. - I don't care.

467
00:44:38.320 --> 00:44:40.200
I deserve to die.

468
00:44:41.680 --> 00:44:44.600
I killed your wife and son.

469
00:44:47.040 --> 00:44:48.679
This is not fucking funny.

470
00:44:48.680 --> 00:44:50.559
It's true. though. No.

471
00:44:50.560 --> 00:44:52.279
I know who was driving the truck.

472
00:44:52.280 --> 00:44:54.160
and I sure as fucking hell
know it wasn't you.

473
00:44:55.080 --> 00:44:57.400
No. but I was there.

474
00:45:17.680 --> 00:45:20.960
My dad wanted information
back from her.

475
00:45:25.800 --> 00:45:27.919
No. no. no. you're lying now!

476
00:45:27.920 --> 00:45:30.800
I saw her. I saw her in the car.
I saw her.

477
00:45:33.680 --> 00:45:35.519
My son.

478
00:45:35.520 --> 00:45:37.200
He's in the back.

479
00:45:39.520 --> 00:45:41.480
'And I saw your boy too.'

480
00:45:42.400 --> 00:45:44.840
I could have saved them.

481
00:45:45.800 --> 00:45:47.480
She begged me.

482
00:45:48.440 --> 00:45:50.879
She begged me to save your son.

483
00:45:50.880 --> 00:45:53.439
'Help my son.'

484
00:45:53.440 --> 00:45:56.320
Please.

485
00:45:57.200 --> 00:45:59.600
Please help my son.

486
00:46:00.520 --> 00:46:03.359
Please.

487
00:46:03.360 --> 00:46:05.720
'And I didn't.'

488
00:46:08.080 --> 00:46:10.080
I let them burn.

489
00:46:16.000 --> 00:46:18.640
I let them both fucking burn!

